# json-repair-rs project generated files to ignore
#  If you want to ignore files created by your editor/tools,
#  please consider a global .gitignore https://docs.github.com/en/get-started/git-basics/ignoring-files.
#  PLEASE DO NOT open a pull request to add something created by your editor or tools

# github/gitignore/Rust
debug
target

# These are backup files generated by rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

# MSVC Windows builds of rustc generate these, which store debugging information
*.pdb

# Generated by cargo mutants
# Contains mutation testing data
**/mutants.out*/

# rustc will dump stack traces when hitting an internal compiler error to PWD
rustc-ice-*.txt
